  EffectDiscription_ENG: '[When Digivolving] You may play 1 blue Tamer card from
    your hand without paying the cost.[Your Turn] When you play a blue Tamer, unsuspend
    this Digimon.[Your Turn][Once Per Turn] When this Digimon becomes unsuspended,
    return 1 of your opponent''s level 3 or lower Digimon to its owner''s hand. For
